(258, 1, '2016-09-27 11:07:27', '2016-09-27 11:07:27', '<p>[su_animate type="fadeInUp"]</p>\r\n<p>[two_third padding="0 20px 0 0"]</p>\r\n<p>[masterslider id="4"]</p>\r\n<h3><strong><em>Mission</em></strong></h3>\r\n<p>The <span style="color: #800000;"><em>JSOS Youth Ministry</em></span> is driven by the heart and movement that support the <span style="color: #800000;"><em>C8</em></span> Campaign of the<em> JSOS Church</em> by reaching out to its youths, empowering them for their holistic <em>Christian</em> growth and secular well-roundedness.</p>\r\n<h3><strong><em>Vision</em></strong></h3>\r\n<p>The <span style="color: #800000;"><em>JSOS Youth Ministry</em></span> has a mature and solid organization with an established culture of worship, intercession, camaraderie, evangelism and discipleship, and leadership and servanthood. It is active in preparing youths for the Second Coming of Jesus Christ.</p>\r\n<h2>Strategies</h2>\r\n<p class="bottom-10">The <span style="color: #800000;"><em>JSOS YUP! Movement ("yes" to Youth Level-UP)</em></span> aims to upgrade the following aspects of the Ministry:</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10">1. Organization<br />\r\n 2. Intercession &amp; Fasting<br />\r\n 3. Discipleship<br />\r\n 4. Evangelism<br />\r\n 5. Camaraderie<br />\r\n 6. Fundraising, Networking &amp; Financial Management<br />\r\n 7. Skill/Talent/Gift-Enhancement<br />\r\n 8. Social Awareness &amp; Community Outreach</p>\r\n<p>[/two_third]</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">[one_third_last padding="0 20px 0 0"]<br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000; font-size: 14pt;"><em><strong>Facebook Feed<br />\r\n </strong></em></span>[fts_facebook id=jsosyup posts=3 posts_displayed=page_only type=page]</p>\r\n<p>[/one_third_last]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_animate]</p>', 'Young People', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'young-people', '', '', '2016-10-12 07:09:55', '2016-10-12 07:09:55', '', 146, 'http://localhost/jsos_wp/?page_id=258', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(259, 1, '2016-09-27 11:07:27', '2016-09-27 11:07:27', '<p>[one_half padding="0 20px 0 0"]</p>\r\n<h3><strong><em>Mission</em></strong></h3>\r\n<p>The JSOS Youth Ministry is driven by the heart and movement that support the C8 Campaign of the JSOS Church by reaching out to its youths, empowering them for their holistic Christian growth and secular well-roundedness.</p>\r\n<h3><strong><em>Vision</em></strong></h3>\r\n<p>The JSOS Youth Ministry has a mature and solid organization with an established culture of worship, intercession, camaraderie, evangelism and discipleship, and leadership and servanthood. It is active in preparing youths for the Second Coming of Jesus Christ.</p>\r\n<h2>Strategies</h2>\r\n<p class="bottom-10">The JSOS YUP! Movement ("yes" to Youth Level-UP) aims to upgrade the following aspects of the Ministry:</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10">1. Organization</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10">2. Intercession &amp; Fasting</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10">3. Discipleship</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10">4. Evangelism</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10">5. Camaraderie</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10">6. Fundraising, Networking &amp; Financial Management</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10">7. Skill/Talent/Gift-Enhancement</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10">8. Social Awareness &amp; Community Outreach</p>\r\n<p>[/one_half]</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Young People', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '258-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-27 11:07:27', '2016-09-27 11:07:27', '', 258, 'http://localhost/jsos_wp/2016/09/27/258-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(260, 1, '2016-09-28 04:34:38', '2016-09-28 04:34:38', '<p class="bottom-20">A collection of<span style="color: #800000;"> <em><strong>JSOS original songs</strong></em> </span>composed by its members. Songs vary from personal to congregational praise and worship songs, fellowship songs, and secular songs. It also features theme songs composed for Christian schools, churches and organizations.</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-20">All sound tracks were arranged and edited by the <em>JSOS Worship Ministry team.</em></p>\r\n<p class="bottom-20"><span style="color: #800000;"><em>Prayer requests:</em></span> Gods provision of higher technical trainings and equipments to improve the production and quality of the soundtracks, and to be able to produce our own music album that can minister to vast people; partners and networks</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-20"></p>\r\n<p>[su_spoiler title="Storms will Cease" class="my-custom-spoiler" style="simple" open="yes"]</p>\r\n<p>[su_animate type="fadeInUp"]</p>\r\n<p>[three_fifth padding="0 20px 0 0"]</p>\r\n<p>[su_youtube url="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=awlsD5HvEaA" width="480" height="320"]</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: #800000;"><em>Composer: <strong>Jose Tacadena<br />\r\n </strong></em><em>Original JSOS Song</em></span></p>\r\n<p>[/three_fifth]<br />\r\n [two_fifth_last]<br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>All storms will be ceasing </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"> <em>The sun will be shining </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"> <em>Trials and problems will be gone </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"> <em>The journey''s peaceful in God''s Son</em></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #800000;"><em>All floods will be dissipating </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"> <em>The grounds will be appearing </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"> <em>Life''s trials will be overcome </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"> <em>God''s grace for us is just awesome</em></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #800000;"><em>When travelling with Jesus </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"> <em>Salvation is enormous </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"> <em>He''s our Rock and Redeemer </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"> <em>He''s trustworthy forever</em> </span><br />\r\n [/two_fifth_last]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_animate]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_spoiler]<br />\r\n[su_spoiler title="Ititik Mo" class="my-custom-spoiler" style="simple" open="no"]</p>\r\n<p>[su_animate type="fadeInUp"]</p>\r\n<p>[three_fifth padding="0 20px 0 0"]</p>\r\n<p>[su_youtube url="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OhaSnhcLC-E" width="480" height="320"]</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: #993300;">Composer: <em><strong>Jose Tacadena<br />\r\n </strong></em></span><span style="color: #800000; font-size: 10pt; font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;"><em>Original JSOS Song</em></span></p>\r\n<p>[/three_fifth]<br />\r\n [two_fifth_last]</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #993300;"><em>Pinagpala Mo ang sangkatauhan </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #993300;"> <em> Ng Iyong ipasulat ang Iyong Salita </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #993300;"> <em> Kinasihan Mo mga pili Mong tauhan </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #993300;"> <em> Sa pagsulat ng kamangha-mangha Mong Diwa </em></span><br />\r\n <br />\r\n <span style="color: #993300;"> <em> Ngayon nga ang Salita Mo''y nababasa na </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #993300;"> <em> Bawat titik ay may himalang halina </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #993300;"> <em> Nagbabago ng puso, nagpapanday ng buhay </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #993300;"> <em> Sa tamang landasin tunay na gabay </em></span><br />\r\n <br />\r\n <span style="color: #993300;"> <em> Ititik Mo po Salita Mo sa puso namin </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #993300;"> <em> Aklat Mo sa puso nami''y s