ler" style="simple" open="no"]<br />\r\n [su_animate type="fadeInUp"]</p>\r\n<p>[three_fifth padding="0 20px 0 0"]</p>\r\n<p>[su_youtube url="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4qMVcwDfwVM" width="480" height="320"]</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: #800000;"><strong><em>Awit 68:19, 20</em></strong></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em> Melody by Pastor Jose Tacadena</em></span></p>\r\n<p>[/three_fifth]<br />\r\n [two_fifth_last]</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #800000;"><em>Purihin Ang Panginoon</em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Ang Diyos nating nagliligtas</em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Na may dala araw-araw</em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Ng pasanin natin (2x) hawak</em></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #800000;"><em>Ang ating Diyos ay isang Diyos</em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Na ang gawa ay magligtas</em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Si Yahweh ang Panginoon</em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Panginoon nating lahat</em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Sa bingit ng kamatayan</em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Hinahango tayo agad</em></span></p>\r\n<p>[/two_fifth_last]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_animate]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_spoiler]</p>\r\n<p>[su_spoiler title="For to me to Live is Christ" class="my-custom-spoiler" style="simple" open="no"]<br />\r\n [su_animate type="fadeInUp"]</p>\r\n<p>[three_fifth padding="0 20px 0 0"]</p>\r\n<p>[su_youtube url="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gWE79ohvfvE" width="480" height="320"]</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: #800000;"><em>Philippians 1:20, 21</em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Melody by: Pastor Jose Tacadena</em></span></p>\r\n<p>[/three_fifth]<br />\r\n [two_fifth_last]</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #800000;"><em>20 I eagerly expect and hope that I will in no way be ashamed, </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>but will have sufficient courage so that now as always </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Christ will be exalted in my body, </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>whether by life or by death.</em></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #800000;"><em>21 For to me to live is Christ and to die is gain</em></span></p>\r\n<p>[/two_fifth_last]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_animate]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_spoiler]</p>', 'Song', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '260-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-07 05:16:27', '2016-10-07 05:16:27', '', 260, 'http://localhost/jsos_wp/2016/10/07/260-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
