(547, 1, '2016-10-08 09:17:31', '2016-10-08 09:17:31', '<p>[su_animate type="fadeInUp"]</p>\r\n<p>[three_fifth padding="0 20px 0 0"]</p>\r\n<p>[masterslider id="6"]</p>\r\n<p>[/three_fifth]</p>\r\n<p>[two_fifth_last padding="0 20px 0 0"]</p>\r\n<p>In the <em>Old Testamen</em>t, <em>Israelites</em> never forget to create <span style="color: #800000;"><strong><em>Praise Memento</em></strong></span>for the victories that God had given them.</p>\r\n<p>These <em>Mementos</em> remind them andtheir children the greatness of God in the hardships they faced in the past.</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #800000;"><strong><em>JSOS Praise Chest</em></strong></span> contains the members'' mementoon how Jesus Christ saved them during theirtimes of trouble -- How Jesus became their hopein their helpless situations.</p>\r\n<p>The <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Praise Chest</em> </span>was submerged to the floodduring the <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Typhoon Ondoy</em></span>. We were not ableto conduct our morning worship in our own Churchduring those times.</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://localhost/jsos_wp/gallery/song/"><em><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"> Storms will Cease</span></strong></em></a> is a video documentation of the said typhoon.</p>\r\n<p>[/two_fifth_last]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_animate]</p>', 'Praise Chest', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'praise-chest', '', '', '2016-10-08 10:00:34', '2016-10-08 10:00:34', '', 434, 'http://localhost/jsos_wp/?page_id=547', 0, 'page', '', 0),
