(586, 1, '2016-10-08 10:16:10', '2016-10-08 10:16:10', '<p class="bottom-20">A collection of<span style="color: #800000;"> <em><strong>JSOS original songs</strong></em> </span>composed by its members. Songs vary from personal to congregational praise and worship songs, fellowship songs, and secular songs. It also features theme songs composed for Christian schools, churches and organizations.</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-20">All sound tracks were arranged and edited by the <em>JSOS Worship Ministry team.</em></p>\r\n<p class="bottom-20"><span style="color: #800000;"><em>Prayer requests:</em></span> Gods provision of higher technical trainings and equipments to improve the production and quality of the soundtracks, and to be able to produce our own music album that can minister to vast people; partners and networks</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-20"></p>\r\n<p>[su_spoiler title="Storms will Cease" class="my-custom-spoiler" style="simple" open="yes"]</p>\r\n<p>[su_animate type="fadeInUp"]</p>\r\n<p>[three_fifth padding="0 20px 0 0"]</p>\r\n<p>[su_youtube url="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=awlsD5HvEaA" width="480" height="320"]</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: #800000;"><em>Composer: <strong>Jose Tacadena<br />\r\n </strong></em><em>Original JSOS Song</em></span></p>\r\n<p>[/three_fifth]<br />\r\n [two_fifth_last]<br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>All storms will be ceasing </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"> <em>The sun will be shining </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"> <em>Trials and problems will be gone </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"> <em>The journey''s peaceful in God''s Son</em></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #800000;"><em>All floods will be dissipating </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"> <em>The grounds will be appearing </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"> <em>Life''s trials will be overcome </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"> <em>God''s grace for us is just awesome</em></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #800000;"><em>When travelling with Jesus </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"> <em>Salvation is enormous </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"> <em>He''s our Rock and Redeemer </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"> <em>He''s trustworthy forever</em> </span><br />\r\n [/two_fifth_last]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_animate]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_spoiler]<br />\r\n[su_spoiler title="Ititik Mo" class="my-custom-spoiler" style="simple" open="no"]</p>\r\n<p>[su_animate type="fadeInUp"]</p>\r\n<p>[three_fifth padding="0 20px 0 0"]</p>\r\n<p>[su_youtube url="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OhaSnhcLC-E" width="480" height="320"]</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: #993300;">Composer: <em><strong>Jose Tacadena<br />\r\n </strong></em></span><span style="color: #800000; font-size: 10pt; font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;"><em>Original JSOS Song</em></span></p>\r\n<p>[/three_fifth]<br />\r\n [two_fifth_last]</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #993300;"><em>Pinagpala Mo ang sangkatauhan </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #993300;"> <em> Ng Iyong ipasulat ang Iyong Salita </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #993300;"> <em> Kinasihan Mo mga pili Mong tauhan </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #993300;"> <em> Sa pagsulat ng kamangha-mangha Mong Diwa </em></span><br />\r\n <br />\r\n <span style="color: #993300;"> <em> Ngayon nga ang Salita Mo''y nababasa na </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #993300;"> <em> Bawat titik ay may himalang halina </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #993300;"> <em> Nagbabago ng puso, nagpapanday ng buhay </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #993300;"> <em> Sa tamang landasin tunay na gabay </em></span><br />\r\n <br />\r\n <span style="color: #993300;"> <em> Ititik Mo po Salita Mo sa puso namin </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #993300;"> <em> Aklat Mo sa puso nami''y sisipiin </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #993300;"> <em> Sa gayon ngalan Mo''y tatatak sa aming gawain </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #993300;"> <em> Mga buhay na liham Mo kami''y tatawagin</em></span></p>\r\n<p>[/two_fifth_last]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_animate]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_spoiler]</p>\r\n<p>[su_spoiler title="Matatapos ang Bagyo" class="my-custom-spoiler" style="simple" open="no"]</p>\r\n<p>[su_animate type="fadeInUp"]</p>\r\n<p>[three_fifth padding="0 20px 0 0"]</p>\r\n<p>[su_youtube url="http://youtube.com/watch?v=MazfZ1R6AAk" width="480" height="320"]</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: #993300;">Composer: <em><strong>Jose Tacadena<br />\r\n </strong></em></span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; color: #993300;">Interpreter<em>: Jehannah Tacadena<br />\r\n </em></span><span style="color: #993300; font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;"><em>Original JSOS Song</em></span></p>\r\n<p>[/three_fifth]<br />\r\n [two_fifth_last]</p>\r\n<div class="right columns">\r\n<p class="lyrics"><em><span style="color: #993300;">Matatapos ang bagyo </span></em><br />\r\n <em><span style="color: #993300;">Araw ay magliliwanag </span></em><br />\r\n <em><span style="color: #993300;">Problema''y maglalaho </span></em><br />\r\n <em><span style="color: #993300;">Papanatag ang paglalayag </span></em><br />\r\n <br />\r\n <em><span style="color: #993300;">Mawawala rin ang baha </span></em><br />\r\n <em><span style="color: #993300;">Makikita muli ang lupa </span></em><br />\r\n <em><span style="color: #993300;">Pagsubok tatalunin </span></em><br />\r\n <em><span style="color: #993300;">Biyaya Niya ay kakamtin </span></em><br />\r\n <br />\r\n <em><span style="color: #993300;">''Pag kasama ay si Kristo </span></em><br />\r\n <em><span style="color: #993300;">Ligtas ang buhay mo </span></em><br />\r\n <em><span style="color: #993300;">Siya ang moog at sandigan </span></em><br />\r\n <em><span style="color: #993300;">Maasahan kailanman</span></em></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>[/two_fifth_last]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_animate]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_spoiler]</p>\r\n<p>[su_spoiler title="RIP (Rest In Praise)" class="my-custom-spoiler" style="simple" open="no"]</p>\r\n<p>[su_animate type="fadeInUp"]</p>\r\n<p>[three_fifth padding="0 20px 0 0"]</p>\r\n<p>[su_youtube url="http://youtube.com/watch?v=2_MhtAlmzpY" width="480" height="320"]</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: #993300;">Composer: <em><strong>Jhesed</strong><strong>Tacadena<br />\r\n </strong></em></span><span style="color: #993300; font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;"><em>Original JSOS Song</em></span></p>\r\n<p>[/three_fifth]<br />\r\n [two_fifth_last]</p>\r\n<p>[one_half]</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #800000;"><em><strong>I.</strong> </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Napapagod ka na ba? </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Sa iyong pagtakbo </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Hinihingal ka na ba? </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Sundalo ni Kristo </em></span><br />\r\n <br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em><strong>II.</strong> </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Nadarama mo ba? </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Ang hapdi ng mga sugat </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Na nakagugulat, ''di masukat </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Kahit ika''y tapat </em></span><br />\r\n <br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em><strong>III.</strong> </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Tubig ng presensya Niya </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Ang ''yong kailangan </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Inumin mo na''t damhin </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Ang Kanyang kalakasan </em></span><br />\r\n <br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em><strong>IV.</strong> </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>''Pagkat papuri </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Ang ''yong panlaban </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Sa lahat ng pagod </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Na ''yong nararanasan </em></span><br />\r\n [/one_half]</p>\r\n<div class="right columns">\r\n<p class="lyrics">[one_half_last]<br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em><strong>KORO:</strong> </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>RIP! Rest in Praise! </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Habang sumasamba, ika''y mamamangha </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>RIP! Rest in Praise! </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>At bawat pagod mo ay mawawala </em></span><br />\r\n <br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em><strong>V.</strong> </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>''Pagkat ang papuri </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Ay nagbubunga </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Ng lakas, </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>At kakaibang saya </em></span><br />\r\n <br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em><strong>VI.</strong> </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Tititigil ang mundo </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Habang sumasamba </em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Kaluwalhatian ng Diyos</em></span><br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000;"><em>Ay makikita nila</em></span></p>\r\n<p class="lyrics">[/one_half_last]</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>[/two_fifth_last]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_animate]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_spoiler]</p>\r\n<p>[su_spoiler title="Sa''Yo Ako''y Mag-aalay" class="my-custom-spoiler" style="simple" open="no"]</p>\r\n<p>[su_animate type="fadeInUp"]</p>\r\n<p>[three_fifth padding="0 20px 0 0"]</p>\r\n<p>[su_youtube url="http://www.youtube.c