(719, 1, '2016-10-12 07:08:56', '2016-10-12 07:08:56', '<p>[su_animate type="fadeInUp"]</p>\r\n<p>[one_half padding="0 30px 0 0"]</p>\r\n<p>[masterslider id="11"]</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #800000;"><strong><em>Strategy</em></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>To usher the congregation into the awesome presence of <em>God </em>through Prayer and Intercession</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #800000;"><strong><em>Monitoring and Control</em></strong></span></p>\r\n<p>Intercessors performance will be checked (attendance, punctuality, cooperation and participation)</p>\r\n<p>[/one_half]</p>\r\n<p>[one_half_last]<br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000; font-size: 14pt;"><strong><em>Goals</em></strong></span></p>\r\n<div class="float-left w-40 top-40 left-40p text-left">\r\n<p class="bottom-10" style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong>1.</strong> To introduce the<em> Lord Jesus</em> to every child that the <em>JSOS Christian Church</em> may encounter<br />\r\n <strong>2.</strong> To teach the children the stories and principles in the Bible, especially life and works of the <em>Lord JESUS</em> on earth<br />\r\n <strong>3.</strong> To encourage each child contacted to follow the teaching and examples of the <em>Lord</em> on a daily basis<br />\r\n <strong>4.</strong> To let the kids feel and experience the love of the<em> Lord JESUS</em> <br />\r\n <strong>5.</strong> To show the kids the importance and the methods of appreciating and loving <em>God</em> through their offerings, prayers, testimonies, talents and obedience<br />\r\n <strong>6.</strong> To train the kids in evangelizing and discipling their contemporaries</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><strong><em><span style="color: #800000; font-size: 14pt;">Vision</span></em></strong></p>\r\n<p class="top-10 bottom-10" style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong>1. </strong> <em><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="color: #800000; text-decoration: underline;">JSOS CC --- A Model Praying Church</span></span><br />\r\n </em><strong>2. </strong> Every <em>Kapamuso</em> has consistent personal devotion to the <em>Lord</em> and has quality prayer life</p>\r\n<p><strong><em><span style="color: #800000; font-size: 14pt;">Reward and Appreciation</span></em></strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">God is glorified, intercessors are encouraged,<em> JSOS CC</em> is strengthened and faithful members are appreciated</p>\r\n<p><strong><em><span style="color: #800000; font-size: 14pt;">Vision</span></em></strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Opening song, Opening prayer, Testimonies, Intercession 1, Devotion, Intercession 2, Announcement and reminder, Personal request/prayer, Closing song/prayer</p>\r\n<p>[/one_half_last]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_animate]</p>', 'Intercession', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '652-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-12 07:08:56', '2016-10-12 07:08:56', '', 652, 'http://localhost/jsos_wp/2016/10/12/652-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(720, 1, '2016-10-12 07:09:15', '2016-10-12 07:09:15', '<p>[su_animate type="fadeInUp"]</p>\r\n<p>[one_half padding="0 20px 0 0"]<br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000; font-size: 14pt;"><em><strong>Goals</strong></em></span></p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10" style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong>1.</strong>  To help in the comprehensive growth of the <em>JSOS Kapamuso</em> by providing for the needed secretarial and office management of the church<br />\r\n <strong>2. </strong> To recruit, train and supervise all the department secretaries of the<em> JSOS Christian church</em><br />\r\n <strong>3.</strong> To assist the department heads in maintaining a thorough departmental record system<br />\r\n <strong>4.</strong> To actively support the<em> JSOS C8 Campaign</em> by maintaining an effective record system relative to its thrusts and a comprehensive <em>C8 Curriculum library</em><br />\r\n <strong>5.</strong> To render an effective office accommodation to church guests and visitors</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #800000;"><em><strong>Activities</strong></em></span></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">-  Hold seminar/training for secretaries, existing<br />\r\n -  Hold seminar/workshop for secretaries, aspirant<br />\r\n -  Basic and advance clerical job clinic<br />\r\n -  News article and feature writing Workshop<br />\r\n -  Blog writing and SNS promotions upload course<br />\r\n -  Basic photography, basic and advance MS tools course<br />\r\n -  Basic corel and photoshop layout and workshop<br />\r\n -  Officework for C8 curriculum and data encoding<br />\r\n -  Start a virtual library access and presentations assistant</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="color: #800000; font-size: 14pt;"><em>Needs</em></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10" style="padding-left: 30px;">-  C.O.T. Writer/Updater<br />\r\n -  JSOSCC FB Publisher/Updater<br />\r\n -  Publications Layout/Assistant<br />\r\n -  Regular encoder/filer<br />\r\n -  Part time encoder<br />\r\n -  Part time office assistant<br />\r\n -  Library assistant<br />\r\n -  Officework for C8 curriculum and data encoding<br />\r\n -  Virtual library assistant</p>\r\n<p>[/one_half]</p>\r\n<p>[one_half_last]</p>\r\n<p>[masterslider id="12"]</p>\r\n<p>[/one_half_last]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_animate]</p>', 'Office', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '681-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-12 07:09:15', '2016-10-12 07:09:15', '', 681, 'http://localhost/jsos_wp/2016/10/12/681-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(721, 1, '2016-10-12 07:09:28', '2016-10-12 07:09:28', '<p>[su_animate type="fadeInUp"]</p>\r\n<p>[two_third padding="0 20px 0 0"]</p>\r\n<p>[masterslider id="13"]</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h2><span style="color: #800000; font-size: 14pt;"><strong><em>History</em></strong></span></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>First called as <em>Music Ministry</em> and first led by <em>Bro. Rey Bonza.</em></li>\r\n	<li>Its name was changed to<em> Praise Ministry</em> through <em>Bro. Christian Tacadena</em> the director that time.</li>\r\n	<li>And was later on changed to<em>Worship Ministry</em>through<em>Bro. Ronald Bolesa.</em></li>\r\n	<li>However,<em>Worship</em>is not limited to<em>Music</em>but should be integrated in our <span style="text-decoration: underline;">lifestyle</span>.<em> </em>Hence,<em>Pastor Jose Tacadena</em>renamed it to<em>Praise and Music Ministry</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h2><span style="color: #800000; font-size: 14pt;"><em><strong>Name</strong></em></span></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>MUSIC</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><em>Music</em> is just one of the many medium to worship God.</li>\r\n	<li>There are three kinds of music - Christian music, secular music and worldly music.<br />\r\n </li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li><strong>PRAISE</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Praise is just one of the various forms of worshiping God.</li>\r\n	<li>We can praise God through music or testifying God''s goodness.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li><strong>WORSHIP</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Worship is so much broader - it''s not limited in music, praising and dancing.</li>\r\n	<li>Worship is life - a Christian''s lifestyle.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h2><span style="color: #800000; font-size: 14pt;"><em><strong>Purpose Statement:</strong></em></span></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>To lead the JSOS Church in corporate praise and worship of God: to inspire the congregation, through the Holy Spirit, to worship the Lord Jesus with all our heart, with all our soul, with all our mind and with all our strength</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h2><span style="color: #800000; font-size: 14pt;"><em><strong>Vision</strong></em></span></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The <em>JSOS Church</em> will become a God-worshiping and praising church - corporately and individually.</li>\r\n	<li>The<em> JSOS Worship Ministry</em> members will manifest the anointing as worship leaders, that through our ministry:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>People will be convicted by the Holy Spirit to come to Christ and make Him as their Lord and Savior;</li>\r\n	<li>Sicknesses and diseases will be healed by God because of the overwhelming presence and power of the Holy Spirit;</li>\r\n	<li>Spiritually weak and backsliding Christians will be revived and restored.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>The JSOS Worship Team will be actively involved in supporting inter-church activities, such as concert, music fest, etc., that is glorifying to the name of our Lord Jesus Christ.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h2><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #800000;"><em><strong>Mission:</strong></em></span></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Spiritual revival in <em>JSOS</em> in worshipping the Lord Jesus Christ - congregationally and individually.</li>\r\n	<li>Every Worship Ministry member must manifest a worship life that is a level higher than those who are not.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>[/two_third]</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">[one_third_last padding="0 20px 0 0"]<br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000; font-size: 14pt;"><em><strong>Facebook Feed<br />\r\n </strong></em></span>[fts_facebook id=475729819203022 posts=3 posts_displayed=page_only type=page]</p>\r\n<p>[/one_third_last]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_animate]</p>', 'Praise and Music', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '700-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-12 07:09:28', '2016-10-12 07:09:28', '', 700, 'http://localhost/jsos_wp/2016/10/12/700-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(722, 1, '2016-10-12 07:09:40', '2016-10-12 07:09:40', '<p>[su_animate type="fadeInUp"]</p>\r\n<p>[one_half padding="0 30px 0 0"]</p>\r\n<p>[masterslider id="9"]</p>\r\n<p>[/one_half]</p>\r\n<p>[one_half_last]<br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000; font-size: 14pt;"><strong><em>Goals</em></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">- As a department of the church, <strong><em>YA</em></strong> must vigorously support every program of the <em>C8 Campaign</em>.<br />\r\n - As individual, each must respond personally to the <em>C8 Campaign</em></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 60px;">Be mature as he/she can<br />\r\n Be an active material supporter of the church<br />\r\n Be an active worker of the church<br />\r\n Be a diligent employee<br />\r\n Be an enterprising entrepreneur</p>\r\n<p><strong><em><span style="color: #800000; font-size: 14pt;">Activities</span><br />\r\n </em></strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">- Careflock after <em>Morning Worship Meeting</em><br />\r\n - Prayer and fasting every <em>3rd Sunday of the month</em></p>\r\n<p>[/one_half_last]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_animate]</p>', 'Young Adult', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '606-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-12 07:09:40', '2016-10-12 07:09:40', '', 606, 'http://localhost/jsos_wp/2016/10/12/606-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(723, 1, '2016-10-12 07:09:55', '2016-10-12 07:09:55', '<p>[su_animate type="fadeInUp"]</p>\r\n<p>[two_third padding="0 20px 0 0"]</p>\r\n<p>[masterslider id="4"]</p>\r\n<h3><strong><em>Mission</em></strong></h3>\r\n<p>The <span style="color: #800000;"><em>JSOS Youth Ministry</em></span> is driven by the heart and movement that support the <span style="color: #800000;"><em>C8</em></span> Campaign of the<em> JSOS Church</em> by reaching out to its youths, empowering them for their holistic <em>Christian</em> growth and secular well-roundedness.</p>\r\n<h3><strong><em>Vision</em></strong></h3>\r\n<p>The <span style="color: #800000;"><em>JSOS Youth Ministry</em></span> has a mature and solid organization with an established culture of worship, intercession, camaraderie, evangelism and discipleship, and leadership and servanthood. It is active in preparing youths for the Second Coming of Jesus Christ.</p>\r\n<h2>Strategies</h2>\r\n<p class="bottom-10">The <span style="color: #800000;"><em>JSOS YUP! Movement ("yes" to Youth Level-UP)</em></span> aims to upgrade the following aspects of the Ministry:</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10">1. Organization<br />\r\n 2. Intercession &amp; Fasting<br />\r\n 3. Discipleship<br />\r\n 4. Evangelism<br />\r\n 5. Camaraderie<br />\r\n 6. Fundraising, Networking &amp; Financial Management<br />\r\n 7. Skill/Talent/Gift-Enhancement<br />\r\n 8. Social Awareness &amp; Community Outreach</p>\r\n<p>[/two_third]</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">[one_third_last padding="0 20px 0 0"]<br />\r\n <span style="color: #800000; font-size: 14pt;"><em><strong>Facebook Feed<br />\r\n </strong></em></span>[fts_facebook id=jsosyup posts=3 posts_displayed=page_only type=page]</p>\r\n<p>[/one_third_last]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_animate]</p>', 'Young People', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '258-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-12 07:09:55', '2016-10-12 07:09:55', '', 258, 'http://localhost/jsos_wp/2016/10/12/258-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
