(785, 1, '2016-10-14 02:33:12', '2016-10-14 02:33:12', '<p>[su_animate type="fadeInUp"]</p>\r\n<p>[one_half padding="0 30px 0 0"]</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #800000; font-size: 14pt;"><strong><em>General Duties and Responsibilities</em></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10" style="padding-left: 30px;">1. Meets at least once a month to discuss matters pertaining to their ministry</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10" style="padding-left: 30px;">2. Plans ways and means to upgrade the church financial and material status, including the strengthening of members'' tithes, offering and other financial commitments.</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10" style="padding-left: 30px;">3. Challenges the congregation on ''giving'' during worship service and other church-wide gathering.</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10" style="padding-left: 30px;">4. Prays intensely for the financial and material upliftment of the church and its members. Holds at least one fasting every quarter for this.</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10" style="padding-left: 30px;">5. Counsels individuals and departments who have been consistently amiss in their giving.</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10" style="padding-left: 30px;">6. Provides financial assistance to church members who have been hospitalized, whose loved ones have departed, and who have encountered emergency financial problems brought by calamities.</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10" style="padding-left: 30px;">7. Provides financial assistance/ love gift to the owners of the borrowed vehicles/equipment.</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10" style="padding-left: 30px;">8. Apportions specific budget for each ministry and department.</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10" style="padding-left: 30px;">9. Provides transportation of our workers to and from their outreach destinations.</p>\r\n<p class="bottom-10" style="padding-left: 30px;">10. Recommends and / or sponsors church workers and leaders to Bible schools and other official trainings and seminars outside the church these are recommended by the Pastor.